Description: Storage device visualization and management tool
 Disk Overview is a GTK3 application for visualizing and managing
 storage devices on Linux systems.
 .
 Features:
  - View local, removable and network disks
  - Progress bars showing disk usage
  - Pinned folders sidebar
  - Desktop notifications for low disk space
  - Open folders in file manager or terminal
